          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Medicaid Tax Fairness Act of 2017</strong></p> <p>This bill incrementally lowers, from 6.0% to 5.5% of net patient revenues, the maximum threshold used to determine acceptable provider taxes for purposes of state Medicaid program financing.</p>]]></text>
